    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those looking for a budget-friendly ride. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some clear coat peeling on the roof. Inside, the cabin shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets, though all major electronics are still functional. While the car runs and drives, it will likely need some suspension work and a tune-up soon to ensure long-term reliability.",
      "price": 19500.0,
