    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty. It's honestly in pristine condition\u2014looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
