      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Titanium Silver. This example is powered by the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The engine exhibits perfect valve clearances and a recently overhauled VANOS system with upgraded seals. Power is transmitted through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. Critical chassis preventative maintenance has been completed, including a structural subframe reinforcement and new rear trailing arm bushings (RTABs). The suspension maintains factory geometry with original Sachs dampers showing zero signs of leakage. The exterior retains its factory depth and gloss, while the undercarriage is free of oxidation. This is a turn-key, collector-quality specimen for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 43800.0,
